name: MealSuggester
0:
”Alexa, ask YummyMeals what I should make for dinner.”
”Alexa, ask YummyMeals what I should feed my family for lunch.”
”Alexa, ask YummyMeals what I should fix for dinner.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: yummy meals
des: YummyMeals will give you ideas of what to make for a meal. This is useful when you have the cook's equivalent of writer's block. Ask YummyMeals for some meal ideas until you get past your block. Remember to cook responsibly, safely, healthily, etc. Let YummyMeals inspire you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
